arbamazepine)." Novartis Pharmaceuticals, East Hanover, NJ.[5] Bailey DG, Dresser GR, Kreeft JH, Munoz C, Freeman DJ, Bend JR "Grapefruit-felodipine interaction: Effect of unprocessed fruit and probable active ingredients." Clin Pharmacol Ther 68 (2000): 468-77', 1767369485);
